  "title": "manager",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Descriptions</strong></u></p><ul><li>Responsible for the organization, planning, control and executive of project.</li><li>Lead and manage a team of operational staff to meet the objectives and targets.</li><li>Establish and implement controls to ensure that work is carried out safety according to the works programme and produce long per works plan.</li><li>Ensure that work is carried out in accordance with the project quality and safety plan, contract requirements, including drawings and specifications.</li><li>Monitor, control; and coordinate site works with the operations team as well as contractors.</li><li>Develop and maintain good working relationships with external stakeholders, including clients,consultants and contracts.</li><li>Support commercial team in handling contractual matters when required.</li></ul>",
